{"name":"Daruk's Protection","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>You invoke the power of Daruk, surrounding yourself in a shimmering red barrier that renders you impervious to harm but limits your abilities. </em></p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.xjGwis0uaC2305pm]{Raise a Shield} or cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.TVKNbcgTee19PXZR]{Shield}</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The first time you would take damage from a source other than persistent damage or an ongoing affliction, it is absorbed by the shield; this does not protect you from any other negative effects of Strikes that hit you or spells that affect you. The spell ends immediately after absorbing damage this way.</p>\n<p>You can Sustain this Spell as a free action triggered by Raising a Shield or casting <em>shield</em>.</p>\n<p>You cannot cast spells or perform Strikes whilst under the effect of this spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.839,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"free"},"duration":{"value":"Sustained"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685222948137,"modifiedTime":1685327981870,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"UgauRj7dQfQ2h5i0","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Urbosa's Fury","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>You invoke the power of Urbosa, unleashing a storm of lightning as you make a wild attack. </em></p>\n<p>Make a Strike against each adjacent creature, using the same unarmed attack or weapon for all of these Strikes; these strikes contribute to and use your multiple attack penalty. The storm then deals 15d10 electricity damage to creatures in the area. Each creature in the area must attempt a basic Reflex save.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.839,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","electricity"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["divine"]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":10,"type":"emanation"},"time":{"value":"2 rounds"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"h3oBRXzTxgiadAql":{"value":"15d10","type":{"value":"electricity","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"reflex","basic":"basic"},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685159944681,"modifiedTime":1685327976485,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"WH8lx5TBWN7ffozN","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
